# AWS Security Group Updater for Cloudflare IPs

This project updates AWS security groups with Cloudflare's IP ranges. Follow the instructions below to deploy and run.

## Configuration

Before deploying, make sure to update the security group and region settings both in the Lambda function (`update_sg_from_cloudflare.py`) and in your Terraform configuration.

## Packaging the Lambda function

To package the Lambda function for deployment, run the following command:

```bash
pip3 install requests -t update_sg_from_cloudflare
cd update_sg_from_cloudflare && zip -r function.zip . && mv function.zip ../



To deploy the configuration using Terraform, initialize and then apply the configuration:

terraform init
terraform apply
